    <h1>Internal Linking</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of creating hyperlinks from one page on your website to another on the same domain. Strategic internal linking <strong>distributes PageRank, builds topical authority, and accelerates content discovery by Google</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
